---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Arnab Sen."
  ogImage={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}og/about.png`}
>
  <div class="simple-page">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>
      Hi, I'm Arnab. I'm a software engineer (L4) at Google, where I work on ads machine learning
      — mostly conversion modeling, calibration, and recovering signal in privacy-restricted
      spaces for YouTube and Search. Before that I interned at Google, GMetri, and Cypherock, and
      studied Computer Science and Technology at IIEST Shibpur.
    </p>
    <p>
      I write about distributed systems, CS theory, math, and the occasional personal essay. This
      site replaced my Hashnode blog — same writing, now self-hosted and markdown-based.
    </p>
    <p>
      Outside of work I compete on Codeforces, CodeChef, and LeetCode, play the occasional CTF,
      and co-authored a paper on classifying classical ciphers with CNNs and Transformers.
    </p>
    <p>
      Find me on <a href="https://github.com/arnabsen1729" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >GitHub</a
      > or <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/arnabsen1729" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >LinkedIn</a
      >.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
